WEBVTT

00:00:59.937 --> 00:01:02.247
ko'tariluvchi binolarni qurish uchun

00:01:02.247 --> 00:01:03.697
mustahkam material

00:01:03.697 --> 00:01:05.137
hosil bo'ladi.

00:01:05.137 --> 00:01:06.299
Odamlar 4000 yildan

00:01:06.299 --> 00:01:08.279
buyon sement yaratishning
turli usullarini

00:01:08.283 --> 00:01:10.283
qo'llab kelishganiga qaramay,

00:01:10.283 --> 00:01:11.279
beton u qadar uzoq

00:01:11.279 --> 00:01:13.909
vaqt saqlanib turmaydi.

00:01:13.914 --> 00:01:15.624
20-30 yil ichida

00:01:15.624 --> 00:01:18.574
sementning tirishishi, kuchli muzlash,

00:01:18.574 --> 00:01:20.334
qizish va og'ir yuklar ta'sirida

00:01:20.334 --> 00:01:23.514
yoriqlar paydo bo'ladi.

00:01:23.514 --> 00:01:25.994
Gap faqat katta yoriqlar 
haqida ketmayapti,

00:01:25.994 --> 00:01:28.394
arzimas darz ketishlar ham 
xavfli bo'lishi mumkin.

00:01:28.404 --> 00:01:30.044
Beton ko'pincha po'lat armatura